	<td bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	<td class="subjectbar" height="20" style="font-size: 8pt;padding-left:10px;" width="100%">
		Improvements to soloing/tasks (January Summit)

	</td>
	
		<td class="subjectbar" align=right style="padding:0px;padding-right:10px;">












		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0 id="io_bveteransm48581_table" 
		
			onClick="setId('48581');showLiMenu(this,'io_bveteransm48581','right',false);" 
			onDblClick="setId('48581');showLiMenu(this,'io_bveteransm48581','right',false);" 
			
		>
		<tr class=clickable>
			
				<td nowrap><a class=subjectbar_text style='font-size: 8pt;'>Options</a></td>
				
			<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
			<td><img src='/i/skins/default/button_options.gif' border=0 alt='Options' title='Options' width=11 height=28></td>
			<td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		</td></tr>
		
	<tr>
	
		<td class="msg_user_cell" width="150" valign=top>
		
			 









<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=1025'  class="auth_text"  style="font-weight:bold;" >	
<span style='color:#9933FF;font-weight:bold; '>Nolrog</span></a>
			<br>
			
			<span style="font-size: 8pt;">
			Community Correspondent<br>
			
				Posts: 11919<br>
				
				Registered: 03-01-2004
				
			</span>
			


			
			<br>
			
				<img src="/i/p.gif" height=8 width=150 border=0 alt=""><br>
				
			<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=1025'>







<img src="/eq/i/icons/correspondent__correspondent/creatures_vox.gif" border=0 alt=""/></a><br>
			


			
			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=Veterans&message.id=48581#M48581">1</a> of 66
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 2879 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>All the rewards I've seen to date have been XP and coin.&nbsp; I'd suggest other types of rewards, such as significant faction hits for hard to raise factions after a long task (such as Freeport Militia); possibly item rewards based on a need you have (you could make the person specifically pick the task he wanted based on the reward he needs.)&nbsp; <BR></DIV>
<DIV>Ideally, the system should check to see if you have the key to a certain zone, before giving you the task for it.&nbsp; Alternatively, you should see the keys required for the task, so you could accept or decline based on that.&nbsp; Another suggestion is to temporarily key someone for the zone while they are doing the step in the task that needs it (but this is open to a bit of abuse.)</DIV>
<P>XP rewards for completing a task&nbsp;should be increased as an incentive to do them.</P>
<P>Add back in the PoP tasks that were removed because they were too hard.&nbsp; Give them a super hard rating, and allow the rewards to be given accordingly.&nbsp; Some people might grab a friend to do that task, or both get the task so they could do it together.</P>
<P>Allow people within the same level to get the same task, so they can do it together.&nbsp; There was one time that friend and I (forgot what class we were each playing, but it wasn't the same) were looking to do the same task, so we could group up and do it together.&nbsp; We weren't exactly the same level, but we were only a level or two apart.&nbsp; We looked and looked but never did find the same task.&nbsp; We wound up getting one that, from the title, appeared to send us to Mistmoore (it did.)&nbsp; However, his task was a lot harder than mine.&nbsp; We completed mine, and not his.&nbsp; I think that was the last time he attempted a task.&nbsp; </P>
<P>Allow tasks to be given out from any task master.&nbsp; It's a royal PitA to have to run to DL to get a task, because you're over 30 (or whatever the level cutoff is.)&nbsp; Also fix the taskmasters.&nbsp; Sometimes, I'd be within the level range, and at the correct taskmaster, and they still wouldn't give me a task.&nbsp; I had to repeatedly hail them before they'd give it to me.</P>
<P>The tasks I've done, concentrated on old world and Kunark.&nbsp; I haven't seen any in other expansions (though I understand the low level Vah Shir ones take you to Hollowshade and the like.)&nbsp; Add in tasks from other expansions, so there's a little more variety.&nbsp; Even tasks that take you to more than one expansion (I think it's time for the whole each expansion must be a separate entity idea to be partially done away with.)&nbsp; I'd love to see a task that gave out a nice reward&nbsp;for collecting something within all the LDoN dungeons (perhaps even bonus LDoN points).&nbsp; </P>
<P>Retune the tasks, so they are more appropriate for the class/level.&nbsp; I got one that asked&nbsp;my enchanter (level 51) to kill 10 wyverns in Skyfire.&nbsp; That was impossible to do solo (had to get help from a necro friend.)</P>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							Nolrog Strongbow - 65th season Ranger of Tunare - Drinal<br><a href="http://qff.jettastarr.com" target="_blank">Quest For Fellowship</a><br>Tamox - 35th season ShadowKnight of Innoruuk - The Combine<br><a href="http://www.noxiousguild.org">Noxious</a><br><br>Sarcasm is a service that I happily (and often) provide.<br>
							</div>
								
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
