<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Klonn wrote:<BR><BR>It has been mentioned on other posts that LDoN AP's might be a good reward (but fitting it into backstory might not be possible).<BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV>Have the tasks for the LDoNs be given out at the Wayfarer camps.&nbsp; This way, you'd still be doing work for them, but now in the context of a task that spans different adventure themes, rather than doing work for them in an adventure.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
