		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>Tying the Task System (or "a" Task-like system) into LDoN opens LDoN points for people that need points, but cannot find (maybe just can't find "tonight") a group for that Theme. LDoNs require 3 people minimum. A Task system with LDoN, perhaps not even requiring entrance to a dungeon, would allow singles and doubles (and more, if the group level range were &gt; 7 or comprised of all, say, Rangers) the ability to still earn points.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>And yes, the point rewards should be less than a standard mission.</DIV>
