<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Better than showing zones for a task, perhaps saying "This may affect the following factions...". Not an all inclusive list, since, obviously, trash mobs could not be included, but still would be a good indicator without revealing too much (if that is a valid reason)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>For soloing - Allow a resist for MOB summoning.&nbsp; OR... Just as a lot of PC spells have side-effects, if a MOB summons, it stuns itself for a short period.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>General:&nbsp;Flag more MOBs outside of OoW as having mana for tapping by Chanters and Necros. I (a necro) have, in recent weeks, actually encountered groups that do not want to go anywhere other than OoW for the stated reason that, with a necro, virtually every MOB can be Mind Wracked.</DIV>
