		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>Great Ideas.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>At least they are considering Kunark pretty much part of the original set now (for inclusion in expansion material).&nbsp; How about Velious too at least?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Placing the TMs way out in nowhere land follows the theme of LDoN.&nbsp; You cant get much further away from a PoK book in the old world than the back corner of LFay without putting it in a dungeon.&nbsp; Then they came along and put the passages to OoW right next to the books almost, go figure.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I could be wrong (its been a while) but at level 39&nbsp;you get more like&nbsp;5 points per adventure,&nbsp;on normal.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>You can be paid in tribute points, just donate your plat.&nbsp; This is not meant to sound glib.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I'd just like to see them revamped period.&nbsp; Fixed to be what they said they'd be.&nbsp; Mainly&nbsp;make them class / race / level appropriate with more choices at each level increment.&nbsp; All that other stuff would be nice too though.</DIV>
