<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Klonn_Darkbane wrote:<BR>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>For soloing - Allow a resist for MOB summoning.&nbsp; OR... Just as a lot of PC spells have side-effects, if a MOB summons, it stuns itself for a short period.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV>Decent idea, on another idea to this is just lessen what mob can summon a PC.. make it so only " caster type " mobs can summon.. Ever wonder why/how a dog can summon you??.. Now mobs with pets are what i would consider " caster type " or even mobs that actually cast spells., but having 95% or more summon these days is&nbsp; discouraging for those whole like to or have to, due to time to play&nbsp;and availablity of groups.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Summoning mobs killed soloing, It made druids and shaman's ask for better healing abilities since their solo abilitiy was pretty much destroyed due to summoning mobs. Necro's have been affected by it also and now ask for better group taps and faster dots. Wizards affected also , asking for better ways to avaid agro and much more damage. Mages affected to as now they cant solo worth a dam since this either. Bards cant swarm kite &lt; well that was kinda sick anyways heh &gt; The list can go on with all classes.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Everyone getting agro reduction on epics, why?, cause heavy healing, dotting, nuking DPS causes a mob to summon a PC .</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I often wonder if the destruction or reduction of soloing abilities has caused the grouping part to be a problem or not..Before the summoning days of&nbsp; " all or most " mobs alot of classes could or would solo , leaving&nbsp;a number of other classes with better oppurtunities to group as there werent 16 classes that HAD to group for xp.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Before you go off and try to find better ways to solo, or group, go back and see what caused people to stop soloing and start looking for group.</DIV>	
